  "title": "Project Manager (Construction) #80335",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Construction</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Project Manager (Construction)</strong></li><li>Working Location: Bedok</li><li>Working Hours: Monday - Friday (9.00am – 6.00pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic + AWS + Variable Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Plan and manage project schedules, milestones, and deliverables; coordinate with architects, engineers, and consultants.</li><li>Prepare and control budgets and cost estimates; monitor spend; approve invoices, variations, and procurement.</li><li>Manage contracts and stakeholders; negotiate and resolve contractual issues; maintain client communication.</li><li>Lead site teams; assign tasks; supervise contractors/subcontractors; conduct regular site inspections.</li><li>Ensure quality, safety, and regulatory compliance; address site issues promptly.</li><li>Identify risks, implement mitigation plans, and handle delays, disputes, and emergencies.</li><li>Track performance and prepare progress reports for management and clients.</li><li>Other tasks as assigned by Management.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Bachelor’s in Civil Engineering, Construction Management, Architecture, or related field.</li><li>5–10 years’ experience managing medium to large construction projects.</li><li>Strong knowledge of local building codes, regulations, and authority processes.</li><li>PMP/PRINCE2 certification is an advantage.</li><li>Excellent planning, budgeting, risk, and resource management skills.</li><li>Strong leadership, communication, and stakeholder management.</li><li>Proficient in MS Project or Primavera; familiarity with AutoCAD/BIM tools.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#80335 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
